des:
Become a master with the 'Unofficial Jean-Claude Van Damme Fact & Quote' Alexa Skill! Gain insight knowledge from the man himself while also discovering more about the Muscles from Brussels! Will be updated weekly, always adding quotes, facts & features!

*Alexa doesn't like Jean or Damme so substitute speaking Jean for Jon & Damme for Dam

*This is a unofficial fan app and is not in any way affiliated with JCVD World or Jean-Claude Van Damme himself
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
